<view class="container"><view class="page-head"><text class="eyebrow">YOUR CORNER</text><text class="title">个人资料</text><text class="subtitle">只展示愿意让同学校友看到的信息。</text></view><view class="avatar-card pressable" bindtap="changeAvatar"><image class="avatar" src="{{avatarUrl || '/images/default-avatar.png'}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view><text class="avatar-title">更新头像</text><text class="avatar-tip">相册或相机</text></view><text class="arrow">›</text></view><view class="form-card"><view class="form-item"><view><text class="label">昵称</text><input placeholder="请输入昵称" value="{{nickName}}" bindinput="onInput" data-field="nickName"/></view></view><view class="form-item"><view><text class="label">微信号</text><input placeholder="只会在你主动发送时出现" value="{{wechatId}}" bindinput="onInput" data-field="wechatId"/></view></view></view><text class="privacy-note">你的微信号不会公开显示，只有主动发送到聊天中才会被对方看到。</text><button class="btn-primary save-btn" bindtap="saveProfile">保存修改</button></view>
